data.title: Contact Admissions
data.meta_description: Get Admissions Office (Counselors & Staff) information for Undergraduate and Graduate studies at D'Youville. Meet your counselor. Get answers to your questions. And apply.
data.text:
The D'Youville admissions office is here to help with information and advice about D'Youville and the admissions process.

If you have a question or need help, contact our admissions recruiters below. They are at the top of their game and have successfully helped thousands of students find their program. If they don't know the answer, they'll connect you with someone who does; from financial aid to the athletic coach on your new D'Youville team.

Contact Us

Email: admissions@dyu.edu

Text: 716-671-3010

Call: 716-829-7600

Hours: Monday-Friday 8:30am-5pm

Send a Document

Fax: 716-829-7900

Mail: D'Youville University Admissions 320 Porter Avenue, Buffalo, NY 14201-9985
